Load Data

data_load <- import("mydata.sav")
# 2. 反向编码SR和TR变量（满分5分）
data_load <- data_load %>% 
  mutate(SR = 6 - SR, 
         TR = 6 - TR,
         health = 5 - health,
         Gender = Gender - 1)

# 3. famhelp、famsup、famtalk、famdec求平均并赋值为FR
data_load  <- data_load  %>% 
  mutate(FR = rowMeans(select(., famhelp, famsup, famtalk, famdec), na.rm = TRUE))

# 1. 去除有NA的行
data_load <- data_load %>% 
  filter(!is.na(PA) & !is.na(VPA) & !is.na(PR) & !is.na(SR) & !is.na(TR) & 
         !is.na(FR) & !is.na(age) & !is.na(Gender) & !is.na(BMI) & !is.na(health))
value_label_map <- data.frame(
  Value = c("AL", "AM", "AT", "AZ", "BE-VLG", "BE-WAL", "BG", "CA", "CH", "CZ", 
            "DE", "DK", "EE", "ES", "FI", "FR", "GB-ENG", "GB-NI", "GB-SCT", 
            "GB-WLS", "GE", "GL", "GR", "HR", "HU", "IE", "IL", "IS", "IT", 
            "KZ", "LT", "LU", "LV", "MD", "MK", "MT", "NL", "NO", "PL", "PT", 
            "RO", "RS", "RU", "SE", "SI", "SK", "TR", "UA"),
  Label = c("Albania", "Armenia", "Austria", "Azerbaijan", "Belgium", 
            "Belgium", "Bulgaria", "Canada", "Switzerland", 
            "Czech Rep", "Germany", "Denmark", "Estonia", "Spain", "Finland", 
            "France", "England", "Northern Ireland", "Scotland", "Wales", 
            "Georgia", "Greenland", "Greece", "Croatia", "Hungary", "Ireland", 
            "Israel", "Iceland", "Italy", "Kazakhstan", "Lithuania", 
            "Luxembourg", "Latvia", "Moldova", "North Macedonia", "Malta", 
            "Netherlands", "Norway", "Poland", "Portugal", "Romania", "Serbia", 
            "Russia", "Sweden", "Slovenia", "Slovak Rep", "Turkey", "Ukraine")
)

# 将data_load$region中的Value替换为对应的Label
data_load <- data_load %>%
  left_join(value_label_map, by = c("region" = "Value")) %>%
  mutate(region = Label) %>%
  select(-Label)
# 4. 替换 region 列中的特定值
data_load <- data_load %>% 
  mutate(region = case_when(
    region %in% c("Vlaamse Gewest (Belgium)", "Wallone, Région (Belgium)") ~ "Belgium",
    region %in% c("England", "Northern Ireland", "Scotland", "Wales") ~ "Great Britain",
    region == "Slovakia" ~ "Slovak Rep",
    region == "Czech Republic" ~ "Czech Rep",
    region == "Macedonia" ~ "north Macedonia",
    region == "Israel" ~ "israel",
    region == "Kazakhstan" ~ "kazakhstan",
    TRUE ~ region
  ))
# 加载 Culture Factor 数据
culture_data <- import("The Culture Factor Group.xlsx")

# 确保 Country 列和 data_load$region 列匹配
# 检查匹配一致性（可选）
culture_data <- culture_data %>% 
  rename(region = Country)  # 重命名为与 data_load 一致的列名

# 合并数据，将文化变量补充进 data_load
data_load <- data_load %>% 
  left_join(culture_data, by = "region")
# 为原始变量添加前缀 "Original_"
original_vars <- c("pdi", "idv", "mas", "uai", "ltowvs", "ivr")
data_load[paste0("Original_", original_vars)] <- data_load[original_vars]

# 创建高低组的变量
for (var in original_vars) {
  data_load[[var]] <- ifelse(data_load[[var]] >= mean(data_load[[var]], na.rm = TRUE) + 
                               sd(data_load[[var]], na.rm = TRUE), "High",
                             ifelse(data_load[[var]] <= mean(data_load[[var]], na.rm = TRUE) - 
                                      sd(data_load[[var]], na.rm = TRUE), "Low", NA))
}
#4. 标准化处理指定变量
variables_to_standardize <- c("PA", "VPA", "PR", "SR", "TR", "FR", "age", "BMI", 
                              "health")
data_load_scale <- data_load %>% 
        mutate(across(all_of(variables_to_standardize), ~ scale(.) %>% as.vector()))

pdi idv mas uai ltowvs ivr

                data = data_load_scale, 
                REML=FALSE, control = lmerControl(optimizer="optimx", optCtrl=list(method="bobyqa")) )
